name: KADO & GOGO's HIDDEN LAB
description:
In a mysterious place, there is a secret project that is being worked on by GOGO. GOGO is creating something, called the 5555. GOGO is not alone, he is accompanied by 0x0000 who is responsible for making sure all machines run properly.

However, in order for this mission to be successful, he needed a large amount of magic power to rapidly add energy to the engine tube.

Thankfully, Kadomeka, who heard the news, immediately found out where they were and came with magic potions and other ingredients to help with this research! Will they manage to complete this project on time?
